title: Council of Nine: Community Leader Elections
body:
The time has come for our Sipherians to decide which candidates (3) will be elected as the Council of Nine - Community Leaders. For more information about the Council of Nine and their roles and responsibilities within the Sipher Nexus program, please navigate to the Sipher Atlas within the following link:

 https://atlas.sipher.xyz/upcoming-programs/nexus-program

Please select one of the candidates below. The three candidates with the highest amount of votes at the end of the election will win.
